//

keep track of score
score starts at 0-0 

user play
bot play


if user clicks on rock 
the bot will randomly select a value
if the random value is rock
then game tied

if the random value is paper
bot wins (function)

if the random value is scissors
user wins (function)

if user clicks on paper 
the bot will randomly select a value
if the random value is rock
user wins

if the random value is paper
game tied

if the random value is scissors
bot wins

if user clicks on scissors
the bot will randomly select a value
if the random value is rock
bot wins

if the random value is paper
user wins

if the random value is scissors
game tied 

repeating actions:
if user play = bot play then game is tied
bot will randomly select a value
bot wins
user wins
game tied


